message.entry: Cannot plot both datetimes and durations on the same chart. Convert one of them to numeric values.
Data must be a single datetime array Y or a list of pairs X,Y.
Cannot plot datetime or duration with other types on the same axis.
Cannot specify multiple tick format parameters.
No value was given for ''{0}''. Name-value pair arguments require a name followed by a value.
Log scale is not supported on time axis. Axis scale is unchanged.
(disabled for figures containing datetime or duration plots)
